statistical model with consideration of preequilibrium
emission, using a consistent set of parameters based
as much as possible on experimental data.

to reproduce the experimental cross sections, but
also to be consistent with other nuclear data as
strength functions, resonance densities and level
schemes. for nuclear reaction data, the corresponding
references are given below under REL-REF. In several
cases the data have been renormalized to recent values
of the respective standard cross sections.
